[infoblox_insights://<name>]
interval = Time interval of input.
index = Select the index in which data should be collected.
global_account = Select the infoblox account for which you want to collect data.

[infoblox_threat_intelligence://<name>]
interval = Time interval of input.
index = Select the index in which data should be collected.
global_account = Select the infoblox account for which you want to collect data.
threat_level = The add-on will collect data for the specified threat level or higher.
confidence_level = The add-on will collect data for the specified confidence level or higher.
historical_data = Select if you want to collect historical data. 
start_date = Provide start date time from which data will be collected. Default will be last 30 days. eg. 2023-02-23 19:00:00.000.